00:16:35.035 --> 00:16:39.164
         Finesse it                  
         and slingshot it back.      

349
00:16:39.206 --> 00:16:41.083
       [man]   He can take            
         the most powerful shot      

350
00:16:41.124 --> 00:16:42.668
